longBusinessSummary: Tianyun International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture and sells processed fruit and beverage products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers various processed fruit products, such as strawberries, apricots, peaches, oranges, hawthorns, coconuts, grapes, loquats, pears, apples, pineapples, and other fruits under the Bingo Time, Tiantong Times, and fruit zz brand names. It also engages in the trading of fresh fruits; production and sale of beverage products, which include energy and fruit juice drinks under the Shiok Party; and manufacture and trading of food machineries. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Linyi, the People's Republic of China.
